                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d105">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Denby</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 107.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-03-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 15, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Li Hung-chang left Taku for Shimonoseki this morning. Foster, Pethick accompanied
                    him He will reach Shimonoseki 18th. Sails under German flag, two steamers. He
                    takes 133 people. Wants to live on steamers at Shimonoseki.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
